Thank you for using the dealer discord bot! This Privacy Policy explains how your data is handled.

1. What Data We Collect
The Bot may collect and store the following data:

Your Discord user ID

Your server (guild) ID

Server-specific configuration data (e.g., shop inventory, balances)

Command usage and interactions

User feedback sent through the /feedback command

In some cases, ephemeral data like verification codes (not stored permanently)

2. How We Use Your Data
We use your data to:

Provide bot functionality (e.g., economy, games, QoL)

Maintain server-specific settings

Prevent abuse and enforce verification

Improve bot stability and features

3. Data Sharing
We do not share your data with any third parties. All data remains internal to the botâ€™s systems.

4. Data Storage and Retention
Data is stored in files (e.g., .json) on our hosting environment

Verification codes expire within 5 minutes and are deleted immediately after use or expiry

You can request deletion of your server's data or your personal data by contacting the bot owner

5. Your Rights
If you are located in a jurisdiction with applicable data protection laws, you may have the right to:

Request access to or deletion of your data.

Opt-out of data collection (by removing the bot from your server).

6. Contact
For questions or data requests, contact the bot owner on discord @jannnn13 (Discord ID: 1145866357829808181).
